snippet.title: Hypnocult Trailer
snippet.description:
New action game from increpare.  Launches 23 Aug, 2019.  Wishlist/buy it on steam :)

https://store.steampowered.com/app/1127680/Hypnocult/

- fast-paced action!
- lots of music!
- 6 different levels to discover and master
- real-glowy vector graphics!
- 3 different modes per level + variable speed settings

Thank you for reading ❤️
